{"article_id":"fTISZrMaZG2aEQgA","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"The suggestion this week from a top Obama campaign official","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"that Mitt Romney may have committed a felony","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"by listing himself as CEO of Bain Capital","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"after leaving the firm","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"was picked apart Sunday ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"with Republicans decrying the remark as the worst type of divisive politics","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"and Obama 's team urging its rivals to `` stop whining . '' Stephanie Cutter , Obama 's deputy campaign manager , originally made the claim Thursday on a conference call .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"`` Either Mitt Romney , through his own words and his own signature was misrepresenting his position at Bain to the SEC ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"which is a felony ,","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"or he was misrepresenting his position at Bain to the American people","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"to avoid responsibility for some of the consequences of his investments , ''","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"Cutter said ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"responding to a newspaper report","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"that Romney was listed as Bain Capital 's CEO after 1999 ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"when he has repeatedly said","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"he left the private equity firm .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"The significance of Romney 's date of departure centers on companies","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"acquired by Bain","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"that later shipped jobs overseas .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Romney claims","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"he left the company","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"before those decisions were made ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"but Democrats point to filings with the Securities and Exchange Commission","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"that indicate","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Romney was still listed as the firm 's CEO .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Cutter 's words drew a quick response from Obama 's opponents ,","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"who said","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"the suggestion","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"that the presumptive GOP nominee had committed a felony","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"was below the office of the presidency .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"Romney himself said in an interview with CNN on Friday","depth":4},{"id":32,"text":"that the charge was `` disgusting '' and `` demeaning , ''","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"and called on Obama and his campaign to apologize .","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"Ed Gillespie , a senior adviser to Romney , echoed that sentiment on Sunday ,","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"saying on CNN","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"the charges reflected a `` say anything '' stance","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"adopted by the president 's campaign .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"`` We now know","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"that this president will say anything","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"to keep this highest office in the land ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"even if it means demeaning the highest office in the land , ''","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"Gillespie said .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"And Kevin Madden ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"newly appointed to a more senior role on Romney 's team ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"said on CBS","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"that the felony suggestion was out of line .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"`` I think","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"it is very troubling","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"that the president would direct this campaign to label someone like Gov . Romney ,","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"who is a very good and honorable man ,","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"as a felon .","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"That 's very troubling , ''","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"Madden said .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Cutter ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"sitting next to Madden on the CBS set ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"she was not calling Romney a felon ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"but merely stating the Bain documents ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"if misrepresentative of his role at the company ,","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"would amount to a felony .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"She refused to apologize for the remark .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"`` He 's not going to get an apology , ''","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"Cutter said .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"`` Just a few months ago in the primary Mitt Romney said to his opponents","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"- who were crushing him at the time -","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"'stop whining .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"' And that 's a good message for the Romney campaign .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Instead of whining about what the Obama campaign is saying ,","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"just put the facts out there","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"and let people decide","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"rather than trying to hide them . ''","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"Chicago Mayor Rahm Emanuel ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"who left his post as Obama 's chief of staff in 2010","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"to run in the mayoral election ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"had similar advice for the Republican candidate .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"`` Give it up about Stephanie .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"Do n't worry about that , ''","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"Emanuel said on ABC .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"`` What are you going to do","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"when a China president says something about you ?","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"Stop whining .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"If you want to claim Bain Capital as your calling card for the White House ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"defend what happened to Bain Capital","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"and what happened to those jobs","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"that went overseas ,","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"those jobs","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"that were actually cut","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"and eliminated . ''","depth":14}],"relations":[{"parent":177,"left":0,"right":176,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":176,"left":118,"right":175,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":113,"right":117,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":95,"right":112,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":93,"right":94,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":92,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":92,"left":1,"right":91,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":2,"right":90,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":90,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":112,"left":106,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":103,"right":105,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":99,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":98,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":96,"right":97,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":96,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":13,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":14,"right":100,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":105,"left":104,"right":19,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":108,"right":110,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":108,"left":20,"right":107,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"